<p>When WWE 2K25 releases on March 7—if you spend at least $100, otherwise it’s available on March 14—, the game will feature a new Showcase mode dedicated to the history of The Bloodline. To help prepare fans for what to expect, 2K has released the full list of matches included in </p>



<p><a href="https://wwe.2k.com/2k25/ringside-report/showcase/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">This year’s showcase</a> mode features three distinct categories of matches where players can either relive, create, or change history. In total there are 16 matches featuring a mix of current WWE superstars and legends like The Wild Samoans, The Street Profits, Rikishi, Nia Jax, Solo Sakoa, 3 Minute Warning, and more.</p>



<figure><p>
<iframe title="2K Showcase: The Bloodline's Dynasty | Official WWE 2K25 Showcase Trailer | 2K" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/tnz8zsUmIBA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe>
</p></figure>



<p>You can check out the full list of showcase matches below.</p>



<h2 id="h-wwe-2k25-showcase-mode-matches">WWE 2K25 Showcase Mode Matches</h2>



<p><strong>Relive History:</strong></p>



<ul>
<li>Yokozuna w/Mr. Fuji vs. Hulk Hogan – King of the Ring ‘93</li>



<li>Rocky Maivia vs Hunter Hearst Helmsley – Thursday RAW Thursday 2/13/97</li>



<li>The Usos vs The New Day w/Big E – Hell in a Cell ‘17</li>



<li>Solo Sikoa vs Carmelo Hayes w/Trick Williams – NXT 2.0 9/13/22</li>



<li>Nia Jax vs Lyra Valkyria – King and Queen of the Ring ‘24</li>
</ul>



<p><strong>Change History:</strong></p>



<ul>
<li>The Headshrinkers vs Steiner Bros – WrestleMania IX</li>



<li>Rikishi vs ‘Stone Cold’ Steve Austin – No Mercy 2000</li>



<li>Umaga w/Armando Estrada vs John Cena – New Year’s Revolution 2007</li>



<li>Tamina vs Natalya vs Carmella vs Charlotte Flair vs Becky Lynch – Money in the Bank ‘17</li>



<li>Naomi vs Bayley – Super ShowDown ‘20</li>



<li>Roman Reigns vs Seth Rollins – Royal Rumble ‘22</li>
</ul>



<p><strong>Create History:</strong></p>



<ul>
<li>‘High Chief’ Peter Maivia vs George ‘The Animal’ Steele</li>



<li>3 Minute Warning vs AOP w/Paul Ellering</li>



<li>The Wild Samoans vs The Dudley Boyz</li>



<li>The OG Bloodline vs Solo’s Bloodline WarGames</li>



<li>The Islanders vs The Street Profits</li>
</ul>



<p>What do you think of the Showcase mode matches for WWE 2K25? Let us know down below, and join more discussions in the official&nbsp;<a href="https://insider-gaming.com/forum/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Insider Gaming forums.</a></p>



